{"tid":1494593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國記者：西方國家雙重標準對待香港暴力示威","createTime":"2019-08-21T16:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T17:16:11.000Z","uid":8814,"like":4,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63d440da90b8c7fe7e7fdd582d970f77007d25f9","tid":1494593,"uid":8814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">條片係點新聞=文匯報出嘅，而家大陸係咁傳呢條片，話美國人都唔幫香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ca_t8SWdpUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fca_t8SWdpUs&d=qWTZpUodHfCf2bB0mbfn0yVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=57600613\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ca_t8SWdpUs</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名美國記者在新聞節目中表示，西方國家在最近香港發生的暴力示威事件上，明顯有雙重標準。西方國家普遍是不會允許在香港發生的這種程度的暴力示威活動在本國出現，一旦出現，必定是以武力收場。他還指出，香港發生的事情是中國的內部事務，而其他國家特別是美國不應該「多管閒事」。"},{"pid":"bec942c19e5bbdaa52cc726f0327ef2ccf469551","tid":1494593,"uid":64131,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"好撚低質呀臭蟲論"},{"pid":"05ba0257b1550aa417e4f36c171dad650bce0c9c","tid":1494593,"uid":301192,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"RT係俄羅斯版嘅CCTV嚟㗎，美你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09955acb860294517b9b7559d472680a7adff24","tid":1494593,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:51:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"3905785edb4bbe2f3f6aef1681123f9e866ea1c0","tid":1494593,"uid":8814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ba0257b1550aa417e4f36c171dad650bce0c9c","tid":1494593,"uid":301192,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:50:37.000Z","msg":"RT係俄羅斯版嘅CCTV嚟㗎，美你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"知唔知個男人係咪美國人？應該係RT訪問個男人"},{"pid":"3d806c06e25cd4008e713698d44a71f3